						You book your tickets to the adventure you want. Wherever you want it. Maybe you want an adventure in Mysore. Or Hyderabad. Perhaps in Jaipur or Delhi. And, of course, there’s always Goa. Choose a place you think you’ll want to visit. (We have ten places you can choose from.) We do the research for you - instantly showing the activities available in the place you want to go. Once you choose your activity, we’ll give you a detailed description and itinerary. (So you know what you’re in for.) And we’ll book the ticket. Then and there. So you can start your adventure sooner. And it saves you energy. 
